node.title: One person dead in Temuka crash
node.description: Police have confirmed one person has died and another has been injured in a crash in Temuka near Timaru.
node.content:
["Police have confirmed one person has died and another has been injured in a crash in Temuka near Timaru.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Claire Eastham-Farrelly\n
", "In a statement, Police said the car went into a ditch on Factory Road at about 4.30pm.", "One person received moderate injuries in the single-vehicle crash.", "Police say Factory Road has now re-opened between Springfield Road and Rise Road."]
